      "body" : "Sometime I wonder if the developper was drunk when implementing this functionnality. Jvm path? -&gt; File/new project setup/structure, then exit, open switch to project configuration File/Project Strusture/project settings/project/SDK AND Platform settings/SDK +  so logical!"
