    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Download and unpack a JDK archive file (.tar.gz) and add it as a SDK in the <strong>'Project Structure'</strong> dialog box ( <kbd>Ctrl</kbd>+<kbd>Alt</kbd>+<kbd>Shift</kbd>+<kbd>S</kbd> )</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/if4hS.gif\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/if4hS.gif\" alt=\"jdk 9 intellij\" /></a>\n<em>click on the gif to enlarge</em></p>\n<p>Also make sure to set an appropriate 'Project language level'. I forgot to do that when creating the GIF.</p>\n<p>Project Structure &gt; Project &gt; Project language level</p>\n<p>For Java 8 set it to 8, for Java 9 set it to 9, and so on.</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 13606162,
      "reputation" : 51,
      "user_id" : 9815250,
      "user_type" : "registered",
