    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>The above responses were very useful, but after all settings, the project was running with the wrong version. Finally, I noticed that it can be also configured in the Dependencies window.\nIdea 2018.1.3 File -> Project Structure -> Modules -> Sources <strong>and</strong> Dependencies.</p>\n"
