    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>For latest version intellij, to set default jdk/sdk for new projects go to</p>\n\n<p><code>Configure-&gt;Structure for New Projects -&gt; Project Settings -&gt; Project SDK</code></p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 1693760,
      "reputation" : 11266,
      "user_id" : 1555615,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "accept_rate" : 62,
      "profile_image" : "https://i.sstatic.net/BwrUZ.jpg?s=256",
      "display_name" : "Marinos An",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/1555615/marinos-an"
    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 0,
    "last_activity_date" : 1595430191,
    "creation_date" : 1595430191,
    "answer_id" : 63037360,
    "question_id" : 18987228,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>On my linux machine I use a script like this:</p>\n<pre><code>export IDEA_JDK=/opt/jdk14\n/idea-IC/bin/idea.sh\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 3311534,
      "reputation" : 727,
      "user_id" : 2784931,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "accept_rate" : 64,
      "profile_image" : "https://i.sstatic.net/RUUe6.jpg?s=256",
      "display_name" : "cptully",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/2784931/cptully"
    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 5,
    "last_activity_date" : 1611757491,
    "creation_date" : 1611757491,
    "answer_id" : 65921104,
    "question_id" : 18987228,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>I am using IntelliJ 2020.3.1 and the File &gt; Other Settings... menu option has disappeared. I went to Settings in the usual way and searched for &quot;jdk&quot;. Under  Build, Execution, Deployment &gt; Build Tools &gt; Maven &gt; Importing I found the the setting that will solve my specific issue:</p>\n<p>JDK for importer.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/4b4pA.png\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/4b4pA.png\" alt=\"IntelliJ 2020.3 Settings dialog\" /></a></p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 10109755,
      "reputation" : 760,
      "user_id" : 7471133,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "accept_rate" : 67,
      "profile_image" : "https://i.sstatic.net/RzjBg.jpg?s=256",
      "display_name" : "Ajay",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/7471133/ajay"
    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 0,
    "last_activity_date" : 1712755710,
    "creation_date" : 1712755710,
    "answer_id" : 78304793,
    "question_id" : 18987228,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>This <strong>worked</strong> for me for Intellij Idea Version 2022.3.3</p>\n<p><strong>File</strong> -&gt; <strong>New Projects Setup</strong> -&gt; <strong>Structure</strong></p>\n<p><strong>SDK</strong>: 1.8</p>\n<p><strong>Language Level</strong>: SDK default(8 Lambdas, type annotation etc)</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/mZb4u.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/mZb4u.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\" /></a></p>\n"
  } ],
